## Task 6: Leaderboard Design

### Retrieving the Top 3 High Scores from Firebase

To get the top 3 players by score, query the `players` node like this:

```javascript
ref.child("players")
   .orderByChild("score")
   .limitToLast(3)
   .once("value", callback);
```

This will return the three highest-scoring players, which you can then display in the leaderboard UI.

